A summary of the scope:

The Minneapolis Public Housing Authority (MPHA) is soliciting bids from
qualified contractors for unit turnover services at 14 scattered-site
properties in North and South Minneapolis. Single-year contract with two
one-year renewal options.

Performance and payment bond NOT required for contracts below $75,000.
Prevailing wage does NOT apply.

Categories:
  - Interior painting (low-VOC latex, contractor's choice manufacturer)
  - Luxury vinyl plank flooring (Shaw, Mohawk, Armstrong or approved equal)
  - Cabinet hardware replacement (brushed nickel, manufacturer's choice)
  - Drywall patching and trim touch-up

Out of scope: HVAC service, electrical panel work, plumbing rough-in.

